import pandas as pd
from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler

df = pd.read_excel("footballmathces_v2.xlsx")

numeric_columns = df.select_dtypes(include=['float64', 'int64']).columns

# Nümerik sütunları standartlaştır
scaler = StandardScaler()
scaled_data = scaler.fit_transform(df[numeric_columns])
scaled_df = pd.DataFrame(scaled_data, columns=[col+"_scaled" for col in numeric_columns])
merged_data = pd.concat([df, scaled_df], axis=1)

# Ölçeklendirilmiş sütunlar dışındaki orijinal sütunları yeni veri setine ekle

merged_data.to_excel("scaled_footballmathces.xlsx", index=False)

import pandas as pd


df = pd.read_excel("footballmathces_v2.xlsx")

    statistics_dict[input_feature] = {
        'mean': df[input_feature].mean(),
        'variance': df[input_feature].var(),
        'standard_deviation': df[input_feature].std(),
        'minimum': df[input_feature].min(),
        'maximum': df[input_feature].max()
    }

statistics_df = pd.DataFrame(statistics_dict)

import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

df = pd.read_excel("footballmathces_v2.xlsx")

# Define input and output columns
inputs = ['match_statistics_home_position', 'match_statistics_away_position',
          'match_statistics_home_total_shots', 'match_statistics_away_total_shots',
          'match_statistics_home_corners', 'match_statistics_away_corners',
          'match_statistics_home_free_kicks', 'match_statistics_away_free_kicks',
          'match_statistics_home_fouls', 'match_statistics_away_fouls',
          'match_statistics_home_offsides', 'match_statistics_away_offsides']
output = 'Total Goals'


# Bar chart for categorical output feature
plt.figure(figsize=(8, 6))
sns.countplot(data=df, x=output)
plt.title('Bar chart of Total Goals')
plt.xlabel('Total Goals')
plt.ylabel('Count')
plt.show()

# Scatter plots for numerical input features vs output feature
plt.figure(figsize=(20, 15))
for i, feature in enumerate(inputs, 1):
    plt.subplot(4, 4, i)
    sns.scatterplot(data=df, x=feature, y=output)
    plt.title(f'Scatter plot of {feature} vs {output}')
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns

data = pd.read_excel("footballmathces_v2.xlsx")

# Important Columns
columns_to_plot = ['away_team_data_national_players','away_team_data_team_value','home_team_data_national_players','home_team_data_team_value','match_statistics_away_corners','match_statistics_away_fouls','match_statistics_away_free_kicks','match_statistics_away_offsides','match_statistics_away_position','match_statistics_away_shots_off_target','match_statistics_away_total_shots','match_statistics_home_corners','match_statistics_home_fouls','match_statistics_home_free_kicks','match_statistics_home_offsides','match_statistics_home_position','match_statistics_home_shots_off_target','match_statistics_home_total_shots']

for column in columns_to_plot:
    if column in data.columns and data[column].dtype != 'object':  
        fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 3, figsize=(15, 5))

        # Histogram
        sns.histplot(data[column], ax=axes[0], kde=True)
        axes[0].set_title(f'Histogram of {column}')

        # Box-plot
        sns.boxplot(data[column], ax=axes[1])
        axes[1].set_title(f'Box plot of {column}')

        # Violin plot
        sns.violinplot(data[column], ax=axes[2])
        axes[2].set_title(f'Violin plot of {column}')

        plt.tight_layout()
        plt.show()

import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np

data = pd.read_excel("footballmathces_v2.xlsx")

# Sayısal sütunların korelasyon matrisini oluştur
correlation_matrix = data.corr().abs()
upper_triangle = correlation_matrix.where(
    np.triu(np.ones(correlation_matrix.shape), k=1).astype(bool))

plt.figure(figsize=(12, 8))
sns.heatmap(upper_triangle, annot=True, cmap='coolwarm', fmt=".2f")
plt.title('Normalized Absolute Cross-Correlation Map')
plt.show()

import pandas as pd
from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split, StratifiedKFold, cross_val_score
from sklearn.preprocessing import LabelEncoder
from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestClassifier
from sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression
from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
import joblib

data = pd.read_excel('scaled_footballmathces.xlsx')

# 'Result' sütununu için encoding işlemi
label_encoder = LabelEncoder()
data['Result_scaled'] = label_encoder.fit_transform(data['Result_scaled'])

# Metinsel sütunları One-Hot Encoding ile encode et
data = pd.get_dummies(data, columns=['weather_data_condition'])

X = data.drop(columns=['Result_scaled', 'Above_2.5_scaled', 'Total Goals_scaled'])
y = data['Result_scaled']

skf = StratifiedKFold(n_splits=10, shuffle=True, random_state=47)

# Modelleme için algoritmalar
models = {'Logistic Regression': LogisticRegression(max_iter=1000),
          'Random Forest': RandomForestClassifier()}

performances = {}

for model_name, model in models.items():
    cv_scores = cross_val_score(model, X, y, cv=skf, scoring='accuracy')
    performances[model_name] = cv_scores.mean()
    print(f"{model_name} Mean CV Accuracy: {cv_scores.mean():.4f}")
    print()

# En iyi modelle train-test bölünmüş veri setini oluştur
X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(X, y, test_size=0.2, random_state=47, stratify=y)

for model_name, model in models.items():
    # Train the model with training data
    model.fit(X_train, y_train)
    
    # Measure train performance
    y_train_pred = model.predict(X_train)
    train_accuracy = accuracy_score(y_train, y_train_pred)
    print(f"{model_name} Train Accuracy: {train_accuracy:.4f}")
    
    # Measure test performance
    y_test_pred = model.predict(X_test)
    test_accuracy = accuracy_score(y_test, y_test_pred)
    print(f"{model_name} Test Accuracy: {test_accuracy:.4f}")
    print()

# Best Model
best_model = max(performances, key=performances.get)
print("Best Model:", best_model)
print("Performance Metric (Accuracy):", performances[best_model])
print()

# En iyi modeli eğit
model = models[best_model]
model.fit(X_train, y_train)

# Test performansını değerlendir
test_pred = model.predict(X_test)
test_accuracy = accuracy_score(y_test, test_pred)
print("Test Accuracy (Best Model):", test_accuracy)

# Save the best model
joblib.dump(model, 'deployable_model_result.pkl')

Random Forest Test Accuracy: 0.5488

import pandas as pd
from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split, StratifiedKFold, cross_val_score
from sklearn.preprocessing import LabelEncoder
from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestClassifier
from sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression
from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
import joblib

data = pd.read_excel('scaled_footballmathces.xlsx')

# 'Above_2.5' sütununu için encoding işlemi
label_encoder = LabelEncoder()
data['Above_2.5_scaled'] = label_encoder.fit_transform(data['Above_2.5_scaled'])

# Metinsel sütunları One-Hot Encoding ile encode et
data = pd.get_dummies(data, columns=['weather_data_condition'])

# İnput ve output sütunlarını ayır
X = data.drop(columns=['Above_2.5_scaled', 'Result_scaled', 'Total Goals_scaled'])
y = data['Above_2.5_scaled']

# Stratified 10 fold cross validation ile train-test bölün
skf = StratifiedKFold(n_splits=10, shuffle=True, random_state=47)

# Modelleme algoritmaları

          'Random Forest': RandomForestClassifier()}

performances = {}

for model_name, model in models.items():
    cv_scores = cross_val_score(model, X, y, cv=skf, scoring='accuracy')
    performances[model_name] = cv_scores.mean()
    #print(f"{model_name} Cross Validation Accuracy:", cv_scores)
    print(f"{model_name} Mean CV Accuracy: {cv_scores.mean():.4f}")
    print()

    # Train the model with training data
    model.fit(X_train, y_train)
    
    # Measure train performance
    y_train_pred = model.predict(X_train)
    train_accuracy = accuracy_score(y_train, y_train_pred)
    print(f"{model_name} Train Accuracy: {train_accuracy:.4f}")
    
    # Measure test performance
    y_test_pred = model.predict(X_test)
    test_accuracy = accuracy_score(y_test, y_test_pred)
    print(f"{model_name} Test Accuracy: {test_accuracy:.4f}")
    print()

# Best Model
best_model = max(performances, key=performances.get)
print("Best Model:", best_model)
print("Performance Metric (Accuracy):", performances[best_model])
print()

# En iyi modelle train-test bölünmüş veri setini oluştur
X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(X, y, test_size=0.2, random_state=47, stratify=y)

# En iyi modeli eğit
model = models[best_model]
model.fit(X_train, y_train)

# Save the best model
joblib.dump(model, 'above_2.5_deployable_model.pkl')

import pandas as pd
from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split, cross_val_score, StratifiedKFold
from sklearn.impute import SimpleImputer
from sklearn.preprocessing import LabelEncoder
from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestRegressor
from sklearn.neighbors import KNeighborsRegressor
from sklearn.svm import SVR
from sklearn.metrics import r2_score


data = pd.read_excel('footballmathces_v2.xlsx')

# Eksik değerleri sütun ortalaması ile doldur
imputer = SimpleImputer(strategy='mean')
data.fillna(data.mean(), inplace=True)

# String değerleri encoding işlemi
encoder = LabelEncoder()
data['weather_data_condition'] = encoder.fit_transform(data['weather_data_condition'])

# Total Goals output sütununu seç ve input, output ayır
X = data.drop(columns=['Result', 'Above_2.5', 'Total Goals'])
y = data['Total Goals']

# Train-test split
X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(X, y, test_size=0.2, random_state=47)

models = {
    "Random Forest": RandomForestRegressor(),
    "K-Nearest Neighbors": KNeighborsRegressor(),
    "Support Vector Machine": SVR()
}

# Cross-validation
cv = StratifiedKFold(n_splits=10, shuffle=True, random_state=47)

results = pd.DataFrame(columns=['Model', 'Mean R2 Score'])

# Her model için cross-validation yap
for model_name, model in models.items():
    scores = cross_val_score(model, X_train, y_train, cv=cv, scoring='r2')
    results = results.append({'Model': model_name, 'Mean R2 Score': scores.mean()}, ignore_index=True)
    print(f"{model_name} Cross-Validation Mean R2 Score:", scores.mean())

# En iyi performans gösteren modeli seç
best_model = results.loc[results['Mean R2 Score'].idxmax(), 'Model']
best_model_r2_score = results.loc[results['Mean R2 Score'].idxmax(), 'Mean R2 Score']
print("Best Model:", best_model)
print("Best Model Cross-Validation Mean R2 Score:", best_model_r2_score)

# Seçilen en iyi modeli eğit
best_model_instance = models[best_model]
best_model_instance.fit(X_train, y_train)

train_r2_score = r2_score(y_train, best_model_instance.predict(X_train))
print("Train R2 Score:", train_r2_score)

test_r2_score = r2_score(y_test, best_model_instance.predict(X_test))
print("Test R2 Score:", test_r2_score)

joblib.dump(best_model_instance, 'deployable_model_total_goals.pkl')
